Pritam Shah was appointed as the Managing Director of our Company on December 29, 1992. He was re-appointed as the Managing Director pursuant to a Board resolution dated February 27, 2015 and shareholders’ resolution passed at an EGM of our Company held on April 3, 2015. He receives remuneration from our Company in accordance with the terms of an agreement dated September 12, 2012 executed between him and our Company, at the time of his re-appointment as the Managing Director. During Fiscal 2015, the total amount of compensation paid to him was ₹ 10.00 million.

